104
00:04:16,122 --> 00:04:17,111
It's beyond astounding.

105
00:04:17,190 --> 00:04:20,557
It is some of the most
impressive reasoning
I've ever seen.

106
00:04:20,627 --> 00:04:22,322
Is there a punch
line coming?
Let's get to it.

107
00:04:22,395 --> 00:04:23,657
I don't know how you do it.

108
00:04:23,730 --> 00:04:27,496
I mean, it's not psychic-ness,
we both know
that's a crock of crap.

109
00:04:28,334 --> 00:04:30,996
But you, sir, are unstoppable,

110
00:04:31,638 --> 00:04:33,196
