112
00:04:36,909 --> 00:04:37,898
Can I tell you a secret?

113
00:04:37,977 --> 00:04:39,501
I wouldn't recommend it, no.

114
00:04:39,579 --> 00:04:40,944
Listen,

115
00:04:41,014 --> 00:04:44,472
you know how everyone thinks
my wife and I have been
separated for nine months?

116
00:04:44,550 --> 00:04:45,983
Yes.

117
00:04:46,152 --> 00:04:48,643
Two years. Two years tonight.

118
00:04:49,022 --> 00:04:51,354
And I'm the one
who keeps trying
to fix the thing.

119
00:04:51,491 --> 00:04:53,220
I mean...
Jeez.

120
00:04:53,326 --> 00:04:56,921
...counseling, therapy,
acupuncture, you name it.

121
00:04:56,996 --> 00:04:59,692
I have tried to
try to try it.

122
00:05:01,601 --> 00:05:03,899
Well, I'm gonna
let you go.

123
00:05:05,071 --> 00:05:06,197
Don't drive.

124
00:05:06,673 --> 00:05:09,574
You know,
I used to be a good cop.
Seriously.

125
00:05:10,243 --> 00:05:12,973
Stunning arrest record.
It was one of the best
in the department.

126
00:05:13,046 --> 00:05:14,980
I caught the
Back Bay killer.

127
00:05:15,048 --> 00:05:16,538
Yes, you did.
I remember it well.

128
00:05:16,616 --> 00:05:18,413
Although I had a tip.
The blue sedan.

129
00:05:18,484 --> 00:05:19,473
Yeah.

130
00:05:21,254 --> 00:05:22,448
