See what I mean?

132
00:05:26,092 --> 00:05:28,526
Come on, you still had to
put it all together, right?

133
00:05:28,594 --> 00:05:30,994
Look, Spencer,
the blue sedan was
the key to the whole thing.

134
00:05:31,064 --> 00:05:32,224
