135
00:05:32,298 --> 00:05:33,959
Yeah, but who had to
run the plates?

136
00:05:34,033 --> 00:05:37,002
And all those numbers
and letters could have
confused many a cop.

137
00:05:37,070 --> 00:05:39,868
Spencer, stop, okay?
I am done.

138
00:05:39,939 --> 00:05:43,932
Here, I want you
to have these.
I don't need them.

139
00:05:44,377 --> 00:05:45,844
