all the credit.

216
00:09:02,375 --> 00:09:05,173
In fact, I don't even
think he can know
we're helping him.

217
00:09:05,244 --> 00:09:07,576
Dude, that's
a good idea, Shawn.

218
00:09:07,680 --> 00:09:09,910
