paid and someone else
gets all the credit.

221
00:09:14,554 --> 00:09:17,250
That, quite honestly,
is some of the best
nut-shelling I've ever heard.

222
00:09:17,323 --> 00:09:18,984
We made a deal.
Yesterday.

223
00:09:19,058 --> 00:09:21,652
We're equal partners.
That means we
collectively decide

224
00:09:21,727 --> 00:09:23,752
which appointments to make,
which cases to take.

225
00:09:23,829 --> 00:09:26,161
