at least for a day,
especially today.

226
00:09:26,232 --> 00:09:27,426
You're right.
Thank you.

227
00:09:27,500 --> 00:09:29,161
It's gonna be a
problem, though.
Why?

228
00:09:29,235 --> 00:09:30,998
'Cause we've already
got a meeting
with the dead guy's widow.

229
00:09:31,070 --> 00:09:32,094
