Ten minutes.

230
00:09:32,171 --> 00:09:33,263
Ten minutes?
Look, don't worry.

231
00:09:33,339 --> 00:09:34,806
I'm gonna do it
in the Chief's office.

232
00:09:34,874 --> 00:09:37,672
Just need you to stand guard
at the door, make sure
no one catches us in there.

233
00:09:37,743 --> 00:09:40,177
It's gonna double
the excitement.
Maybe triple it.

234
00:09:40,246 --> 00:09:42,305
Now, come on, who's in?

235
00:09:42,381 --> 00:09:43,370
Don't fool around.

236
00:09:43,449 --> 00:09:45,440
You know I can't
hold my hand like
this for very long.

237
00:09:45,518 --> 00:09:48,385
Gus, I get very
poor circulation to
the limbic regions.

238
00:09:52,858 --> 00:09:54,519
And now my
pinky's going numb.

239
00:09:54,594 --> 00:09:57,961
I guess everything started
to change at the beginning
of last summer.

240
00:09:58,130 --> 00:10:00,360
He partnered with his
old friend, Hugo,

241
00:10:00,433 --> 00:10:02,162
and they finally
got accepted
for eight months

242
00:10:02,234 --> 00:10:04,668
on the new digital telescope
at the Space Center.

243
