00:10:07,373 --> 00:10:09,568
suddenly, Bryant
started to work
really long hours.

245
00:10:09,642 --> 00:10:10,836
I see.

246
00:10:12,144 --> 00:10:13,338
What do you think of this?

247
00:10:13,412 --> 00:10:14,401
I like it.

248
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:17,813
