that's when he started
feeling sick, Mary?

250
00:10:21,253 --> 00:10:23,278
Not sick,
just a little off.

251
00:10:23,356 --> 00:10:25,551
Oh! We did cancel
our Fourth of July trip,

252
00:10:25,625 --> 00:10:27,559
so I guess it was
around that time.

253
00:10:27,660 --> 00:10:29,685
I'm sorry,
something is really
bugging me.

254
00:10:29,762 --> 00:10:31,354
Your name is Lassiter, too?

255
00:10:31,430 --> 00:10:34,126
Yes, that's correct.
Carlton Lassiter.

256
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:38,068
But you're not affiliated
with the detective Carlton
Lassiter who I met before?

257
00:10:38,137 --> 00:10:40,867
Not in any way,
