Different department.

258
00:10:40,940 --> 00:10:43,534
Matter of fact,
I spell mine with a "K."

259
00:10:43,843 --> 00:10:45,105
Two of them.

260
00:10:46,245 --> 00:10:49,681
Mary, is there anything
you're leaving out?

261
00:10:50,349 --> 00:10:52,613
