301
00:12:25,444 --> 00:12:26,934
I mean, look at him.

302
00:12:28,380 --> 00:12:29,506
Okay, I'm in.

303
00:12:29,782 --> 00:12:30,806
You're what?

304
00:12:30,883 --> 00:12:32,009
What do you got?

305
00:12:41,627 --> 00:12:43,788
My Dad is not answering
