311
00:12:54,473 --> 00:12:55,565
It's the Bryant Vallery case.

312
00:12:55,641 --> 00:12:56,699
The one from this morning?

313
00:12:56,776 --> 00:12:57,800
And the rest
of the week.

314
00:12:57,877 --> 00:13:01,176
