371
00:16:09,468 --> 00:16:10,958
What are we doing.
Dude, we're undercover.

372
00:16:11,036 --> 00:16:12,264
We are not
undercover.
Sure, we are.

373
00:16:12,338 --> 00:16:13,532
I'm the employee,
you're the customer.

374
00:16:13,605 --> 00:16:14,594
I am the customer.

375
00:16:14,673 --> 00:16:16,334
See? You're already
in character, like
Don Cheadle!

376
00:16:16,408 --> 00:16:17,568
I'm not involved
with this case.

377
00:16:17,643 --> 00:16:19,076
I only need you
for a minute.

378
00:16:19,144 --> 00:16:20,839
Like when Kenickie
needed Danny Zuko.

379
00:16:20,913 --> 00:16:23,006
And you get to be Travolta
in the analogy.

380
00:16:23,082 --> 00:16:24,947
Tomorrow, they're training me
on the motion simulator.

381
00:16:25,017 --> 00:16:27,747
Tell me you've never wanted
