of those things buck-naked.

382
00:16:27,820 --> 00:16:28,878
No, I haven't.

383
00:16:28,954 --> 00:16:29,943
Sure you have.

384
00:16:30,022 --> 00:16:31,319
I'm only here for
a few minutes, anyway.

385
00:16:31,390 --> 00:16:32,448
That's all I need.

386
00:16:32,524 --> 00:16:34,856
SHAWN: Look, there's
this creepy janitor
