planetarium girl.

388
00:16:37,062 --> 00:16:38,188
You are not
grilling Jessica.

389
00:16:38,263 --> 00:16:40,754
She's just interning
here until she gets
her college units.

390
00:16:40,833 --> 00:16:41,959
Jessica?
Yeah!

391
00:16:42,034 --> 00:16:43,899
How do you know
her name is...

392
00:16:44,036 --> 00:16:45,025
(GASPS)

393
00:16:45,170 --> 00:16:47,070
Oh, Gus.
What?

394
00:16:47,139 --> 00:16:50,074
You haven't been coming
here on Thursdays
to study the stars.

395
00:16:50,142 --> 00:16:51,632
You've been coming
here for her!

396
00:16:51,710 --> 00:16:52,870
Do you love her?
Shut up, Shawn.

397
00:16:52,945 --> 00:16:54,071
You're in love with her.
Shut up, Shawn.

398
00:16:54,146 --> 00:16:55,443
I'm gonna go
hook you guys up.
No, Shawn.

399
00:16:55,514 --> 00:16:57,505
She is my co-worker
and I have the inside track.

400
00:16:57,583 --> 00:16:59,346
Listen, there are ways
to go about doing this.

401
00:16:59,418 --> 00:17:01,352
You don't just
walk up to somebody at
their place of employment

402
00:17:01,420 --> 00:17:03,513
and start working them over.
You've got to have a plan.

403
00:17:03,589 --> 00:17:05,250
Do you have a plan?
Of course I have a plan.

404
00:17:05,324 --> 00:17:07,690
Well, would you mind
clueing me in, please?

405
00:17:07,860 --> 00:17:09,350
All right, listen.

406
00:17:11,230 --> 00:17:12,822
She's been through
a lot lately.
She just had...

407
00:17:12,898 --> 00:17:14,422
Broke up with
her boyfriend.

408
00:17:14,500 --> 00:17:16,365
How'd you know that?
It's my curse, apparently.

409
00:17:16,435 --> 00:17:19,700
Well, since she's just
off a break-up,
I gotta move gradually.

410
00:17:19,772 --> 00:17:21,933
Just go over there
and ask her out.
Get her digits.

411
00:17:22,007 --> 00:17:25,499
Shawn, this is a quality girl.
