415
00:17:32,084 --> 00:17:33,813
Yes. Gus is
a regular.

416
00:17:33,886 --> 00:17:34,875
That's right.

417
00:17:34,953 --> 00:17:36,818
You know,
I went to high school
with him.

418
00:17:36,889 --> 00:17:39,687
Of course, I didn't hang out
with cool kids like Gus
in high school.

419
00:17:39,758 --> 00:17:42,249
He was a CIF
wrestling champion
back then.

420
00:17:42,327 --> 00:17:43,351
Really?

421
00:17:43,429 --> 00:17:45,693
True as toast.
And in college,
he was a Heisman candidate

422
00:17:45,764 --> 00:17:47,026
