in the newspapers, man.

424
00:17:49,868 --> 00:17:50,892
You're kidding.

425
00:17:50,969 --> 00:17:53,164
Well, he is, actually.
I don't kid, ever.

426
00:17:53,472 --> 00:17:56,908
I idolize this guy.
The coolest dude
I have ever known.

427
00:17:56,975 --> 00:17:59,876
Wow, Gus, it seems
